#: private-components/swingui/src/main/java/org/limewire/ui/swing/mainframe/AboutWindow.java:131
msgid ""
"Here at the WireShare project, we believe in the value of hard work.  "
"Because we are in no way a formally-organised or structured enterprise, "
"because we hold no assets to speak of, because we do not control or intend "
"to control the Gnutella network, and because we subscribe to the pro bono "
"ethos, authorship credit is the major benefit that our contributors derive "
"from their activity.  Since our primary mission is to maintain bona fide "
"continuity and fidelity with the final version of the LimeWire Gnutella "
"servent software, and in our role as the final fork and continuation of that "
"project, we have no intention of diminishing the credit due to their "
"contributors.  On the contrary, this page serves to memorialise the "
"developers, testers, technical writers, and designers of Lime Wire LLC:"
msgstr ""

#. previous developers
#: private-components/swingui/src/main/java/org/limewire/ui/swing/mainframe/AboutWindow.java:188
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In addition, the following individuals had worked on the LimeWire team but "
"had transitioned to other projects prior to its discontinuation:"
msgstr ""
"Les personnes suivantes ont également travaillé avec l’équipe de WireShare "
"dans le passé mais travaillent désormais sur d’autres projets :"

#. open source contributors
#: private-components/swingui/src/main/java/org/limewire/ui/swing/mainframe/AboutWindow.java:281
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"LimeWire open source contributors have provided significant code and many "
"bug fixes, ideas, research, etc. to the project as well. Those listed below "
"have either written code that is distributed with every version of WireShare "
"(previously LimeWire), have identified serious bugs in the code, or both:"
msgstr ""
"Les contributeurs au logiciel libre WireShare ont fourni de précieux codes "
"et ont également fourni de nombreuses réparations de bogues, idées, "
"recherches, etc. pour le projet. Les personnes citées ci-dessous ont écrit "
"un code désormais distribué dans chaque version de WireShare ou identifié de "
"sérieuses anomalies dans le code, voire les deux :"

#. internationalization contributors
#: private-components/swingui/src/main/java/org/limewire/ui/swing/mainframe/AboutWindow.java:354
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We would also like to thank the many contributors to the "
"internationalization project, both for the WireShare application and for the "
"LimeWire web site, which has, unfortunately, been taken down."
msgstr ""
"WireShare aimerait également remercier les nombreux collaborateurs au projet "
"d’internationalisation, aussi bien pour l’application que pour le site "
"Internet de WireShare."

#. community VIPs
#: private-components/swingui/src/main/java/org/limewire/ui/swing/mainframe/AboutWindow.java:358
msgid ""
"Several colleagues in the Gnutella community merit special thanks. These "
"include:"
msgstr ""
"Certains de nos collègues de la communauté Gnutella méritent tout "
"particulièrement nos remerciements :"

#. conclusion
#: private-components/swingui/src/main/java/org/limewire/ui/swing/mainframe/AboutWindow.java:380
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The makers of WireShare would like to extend their sincere thanks to those "
"developers, users, and all others who have contributed their ideas to the "
"project. Without our valued users, the Gnutella Peer-to-Peer Network would "
"not exist."
msgstr ""
"Enfin, WireShare voudrait remercier les développeurs, les utilisateurs et "
"tous ceux qui ont partagé leurs idées avec le projet. Sans les utilisateurs "
"de WireShare, le réseau P2P n’existerait pas."

#: private-components/swingui/src/main/java/org/limewire/ui/swing/mainframe/AboutWindow.java:385
